// Test Results Data const loadTestData = [ { time: '0s', responseTime: 150 }, { time: '10s', responseTime: 180 }, { time: '20s', responseTime: 200 }, { time: '30s', responseTime: 190 }, { time: '40s', responseTime: 195 }, { time: '50s', responseTime: 200 } ]; const stressTestData = [ { time: '0s', cpuUsage: 20 }, { time: '10s', cpuUsage: 40 }, { time: '20s', cpuUsage: 60 }, { time: '30s', cpuUsage: 80 }, { time: '40s', cpuUsage: 90 }, { time: '50s', cpuUsage: 90 } ]; const spikeTestData = [ { category: 'Success', value: 80 }, { category: 'Failed', value: 20 } ]; const soakTestData = [ { time: '0h', memory: 500 }, { time: '0.5h', memory: 500 }, { time: '1h', memory: 500 }, { time: '1.5h', memory: 500 }, { time: '2h', memory: 500 } ]; const performanceTrendsData = [ { day: 'Mon', responseTime: 180, successRate: 98.0 }, { day: 'Tue', responseTime: 200, successRate: 97.0 }, { day: 'Wed', responseTime: 190, successRate: 96.0 }, { day: 'Thu', responseTime: 208, successRate: 97.5 }, { day: 'Fri', responseTime: 195, successRate: 95.0 }, { day: 'Sat', responseTime: 195, successRate: 96.5 }, { day: 'Sun', responseTime: 200, successRate: 98.0 } ]; // System Health Data const systemHealthData = [ { name: 'Overall Health', value: 85, color: '#10B981' }, { name: 'Remaining', value: 15, color: '#8B5CF6' } ]; const performanceScoreData = [ { name: 'Performance Score', value: 92, color: '#10B981' }, { name: 'Remaining', value: 8, color: '#8B5CF6' } ]; const stabilityIndexData = [ { name: 'Stability Index', value: 78, color: '#F59E0B' }, { name: 'Remaining', value: 22, color: '#8B5CF6' } ]; const recentTests = [ { type: "Load Test Completed", details: "100 users, 200ms avg response time", timestamp: "2 minutes ago", status: "success", icon: CheckCircle }, { type: "Stress Test Warning", details: "High CPU usage detected at 90%", timestamp: "15 minutes ago", status: "warning", icon: AlertTriangle }, { type: "Spike Test Failed", details: "20% failure rate under load spike", timestamp: "1 hour ago", status: "error", icon: X } ]; const getStatusColor = (status) => { switch (status) { case 'success': return '#10B981'; case 'warning': return '#F59E0B'; case 'error': return '#EF4444'; default: return '#6B7280'; } }; const getStatusIcon = (status) => { switch (status) { case 'success': return CheckCircle;
